Package algorithms

Class SortAlgorithm

java.lang.Object
algorithms.SortAlgorithm
Direct Known Subclasses:
BubbleSort, HeapSort, InsertionSort, MergeSort, QuickSort
public abstract class SortAlgorithm extends Object
Abstract class for all sorting algorithms to extend. This class contains the methods that are common to all sorting algorithms. This class also contains the methods that are used to test the sorting algorithms.
Author:
Gage Carpenter
